---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../index.css';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - CozyPixels" description="Privacy Policy for CozyPixels desktop app and website.">
  <main style="padding: 120px 24px 80px; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;">
    <div style="max-width: 720px; width: 100%; text-align: left; line-height: 1.7;">
      <h1 class="font-display" style="font-size: 3.5rem; color: #1e2444; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 850; letter-spacing: -0.04em;">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: #7a84a0; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; font-family: var(--font-label); letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase;">Last updated: May 31, 2026</p>
      
      <p style="color: #52607a; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">At CozyPixels, your privacy is our priority. This Privacy Policy outlines our practices regarding data collection and usage when you visit our website or use our Desktop Application and Chrome Extension.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display" style="font-size: 1.8rem; color: #2f365e; margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; font-weight: 700;">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p style="color: #626d86; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">We believe in keeping things simple. The CozyPixels Desktop App, Chrome Extension, and Website do <strong style="color: #1e2444;">not</strong> collect, store, or transmit any personally identifiable information (PII) to our servers. Any preferences, such as your favorite wallpapers or Pomodoro timer settings, are stored locally on your device.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display" style="font-size: 1.8rem; color: #2f365e; margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; font-weight: 700;">2. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p style="color: #626d86; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Our website may use basic analytics (like Vercel Analytics) to monitor overall site traffic and performance. These tools collect anonymized data, such as general geographic regions and browser types, but do not track individual users.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display" style="font-size: 1.8rem; color: #2f365e; margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; font-weight: 700;">3. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p style="color: #626d86; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated revision date.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display" style="font-size: 1.8rem; color: #2f365e; margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; font-weight: 700;">4. Contact Us</h2>
      <p style="color: #626d86; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@cozypixels.app" style="color: var(--color-primary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">privacy@cozypixels.app</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
